                            <comment id="13275999" author="phunt" created="Tue, 15 May 2012 17:16:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think we need to revert this commit. The patch as committed introduces a socket leak - there is a race condition where 1) the run method could be processing a socket operation that throws an ioexception, and 2) the shutdown flag being set. As a result we might not close the socket.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
